0.12.0+1.0

- Initial community recipe: launches the iaiops 0.12.0 OCI image via Podman.
- Read-first, hardened container (read-only rootfs, all caps dropped,
  no-new-privileges); state persists in /services_rw/iaiops.
- Site config (edition/profile, MCP transport, account/IP allowlist) via
  /services_rw/iaiops/iaiops.env; protocol targets via /services_rw/iaiops/config.yaml.
